</div>                    

<div class="level4">
<span class="level5 pli-lang">
<a href="/sc/?q=bu-as1-7#2.2">Adhikaraṇasamatha 1.</a> <a href="/sc/?q=bu-pm#247.0">pm</a> Sammukhāvinayo dātabbo.
